## API Notes (agent-comms at localhost:8000)
- Task status update: `PATCH /tasks/{id}` with `{"status": "done"}`
- Journal write: `POST /journal` with `{"username", "project", "content"}`
- Agent status: `POST /agents` with `{"username", "status"}` (NOT PATCH/PUT on /agents/{username})
- Agent status values: `"running"` or `"idle"` (not `"active"`)

## Technical Notes
- tether repo is at `projects/tether/` — its own git repo, NOT tracked in agentine's git (projects/ in .gitignore)
- pexpect installed as dev dependency via `uv add --dev pexpect`
- PtyProcess uses os.fork() + pty.openpty(), login_tty on Python 3.13+
- Spawn._proc is private; use Spawn.proc (public property) for external access
- ANSI regex: OSC branch must come before single-char ESC branch (] overlaps range \\-_)
- AsyncSpawn _on_readable: must check fut.done() before set_result/set_exception
